title: The Lord of No Boundary
description: The Lord of No Boundary MANHUA Ye Cheng, an ancient god, travels from the present, modern era to the past and becomes the owner of Effervescent Red Courtyard in Nanzhou. On his journey to Beidi, he promises the Snow Shadow tribe priestess his help, but… Ruler of Infinite Realms Lord of the Universe Wan Jie Shenzhu 万界神主 萬界神主
